query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `user_license_transactions` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,
  `licenseId` int NOT NULL,
  `transactionType` enum('purchase','renewal','upgrade','downgrade','cancellation') NOT NULL,
  `amount` decimal(10,2) NOT NULL,
  `currency` varchar(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'EUR',
  `paymentMethod` enum('stripe','invoice','partner') NOT NULL,
  `paymentStatus` enum('pending','completed','failed','refunded') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'pending',
  `stripePaymentIntentId` varchar(255),
  `transactionDate` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  INDEX `license_transactions_license_idx` (`licenseId`),
  INDEX `license_transactions_date_idx` (`transactionDate`),
  INDEX `license_transactions_status_idx` (`paymentStatus`)
);
